ientCSSSelectors" rel=3D"nofollow ugc">more efficient selectors</a> make yo=
ur page render faster.</p>
<p>Another thing is to always put elements (e.g. =E2=80=9Cp, a, h1=E2=80=9D=
) and generic classes (e.g. =E2=80=9Clast=E2=80=9D) before the other rules,=
